### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "fullName": "Asha Rao", "email": "asha@example.com", "password": "secret1", "phone": "9999999999" }

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@wingify.com", "password": "admin123" }

### List products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products?q=serum&categoryId=1

### Add to cart (replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{ "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }

### Checkout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/checkout
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{ "shippingAddress": "12 MG Road, Mumbai", "paymentMethod": "COD" }
